brief: Dato' Sri Haji Mohammad Najib bin Tun Haji Abdul Razak is the sixth and current Prime Minister of Malaysia. He was sworn into the position on 3 April 2009 to succeed Abdullah Ahmad Badawi.
name: Najib Razak

brief: Tan Sri Datuk Seri Panglima Haji Musa bin Haji Aman is the 14th and current Chief Minister of the state of Sabah in Malaysia, in office since 2003
name: Musa Aman

brief: Mahathir bin Mohamad is a Malaysian politician who was the fourth Prime Minister of Malaysia from 1981 to 2003, making him longest-serving holder of that office.
name: Mahathir Mohamad
